        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer375998762" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1888934712184918803">This is hard to rate because the book is loaded with valuable insights. There are several quotes that will apply to your life today.<br/><br/>That said, it was very hard to read. It is boring beyond belief. It took me months to get through it because I could only take a few pages at a time before my mind wondered off.<br/><br/>I don&apos;t think I got all there is to get from it in one read. This is more of a book that needs to be studied. Perhaps leave is laying on the coffee table and read a page or two a day with a h</span>
  <span id="freeText1888934712184918803" style="display:none">This is hard to rate because the book is loaded with valuable insights. There are several quotes that will apply to your life today.<br /><br />That said, it was very hard to read. It is boring beyond belief. It took me months to get through it because I could only take a few pages at a time before my mind wondered off.<br /><br />I don't think I got all there is to get from it in one read. This is more of a book that needs to be studied. Perhaps leave is laying on the coffee table and read a page or two a day with a high lighter. <br /><br />I will probably read it many times over to let all the wisdom sink in, but this same information could be easily condensed into another book with fewer words, and better editing to appeal to modern day readers. </span>
